{
  "texts": [
    "Training, in particular, is strongly associated with new job responsibilities, suggesting that these programs may be designed to help workers handle new responsibilities introduced by AI tools.",
    "The importance of task creation for the impact of AI chatbots on workloads supports key theoretical predictions for how automation technologies may reinstate the demand for labor in the production process (Acemoglu and Restrepo, 2019; Autor et al., 2024).",
    "To further understand how AI chatbots affect the nature of work, we asked respondents to describe the new job tasks they perform as a result of AI chatbots.",
    "In Appendix B.3, we categorize the free-text responses into common new tasks associated with AI chatbots in each occupation.",
    "AI chatbots have generated new job tasks for workers across all 11 occupations, with 50% to 95% of these directly linked to AI use."
  ]
}